\c 22
\s UBalaki loBalami
\p
\v 1 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebesuka\x + 26.3,63; 31.12; 33.48,50; 35.1; 36.13.\x*, bamisa inkamba emagcekeni akoMowabi, nganeno kweJordani, eJeriko\x + 26.3,63; 31.12; 33.48,50; 35.1; 36.13.\x*.
\v 2 UBalaki indodana kaZipori wasebona konke uIsrayeli ayekwenze kumaAmori.
\v 3 UMowabi wasesesaba kakhulu ubuso babantu, ngoba babebanengi\x + Eks. 15.15.\x*. UMowabi wasetshaywa luvalo ngenxa yabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + Eks. 1.12.\x*.
\v 4 UMowabi wasesithi ebadaleni beMidiyani\x + 22.7; 25.18; 31.8. Josh. 13.21.\x*: Khathesi lelibandla lizakhotha konke okusihanqileyo, njengenkabi ikhotha utshani bedlelo. Njalo uBalaki indodana kaZipori wayeyinkosi yakoMowabi ngalesosikhathi.
\v 5 Wasethuma izithunywa kuBalami indodana kaBeyori\x + Dute. 23.4. Josh. 13.22; 24.9. Hlu. 11.25. Neh. 13.1,2. Mika 6.5. 2 Pet. 2.15. Juda 11. Isam. 2.14.\x* ePethori\x + 23.7. Dute. 23.4.\x* eliseduze lomfula welizwe labantwana babantu bakhe, ukumbiza, esithi: Khangela, abantu baphumile eGibhithe. Khangela, basibekele ubuso bomhlaba, futhi sebehlala maqondana lami.
\v 6 Khathesi-ke, ake uze, ngiqalekisela lababantu\x + 23.7.\x*, ngoba balamandla kulami; mhlawumbe ngingaba lamandla okuthi sibatshaye, lokuthi ngibaxotshe elizweni, ngoba ngiyazi ukuthi lowo ombusisayo ubusisiwe, lalowo omqalekisayo uqalekisiwe.
\v 7 Abadala beMowabi labadala beMidiyani basebehamba belembadalo yokuvumisa esandleni sabo; bafika kuBalami, bakhuluma kuye amazwi kaBalaki\x + 23.23. 1 Sam. 9.7,8.\x*.
\v 8 Wasesithi kubo: Lalani lapha lobubusuku, njalo ngizalilethela ilizwi, njengalokhu iN\nd kosi\nd* ezakutsho kimi\x + 22.19.\x*. Iziphathamandla zakoMowabi zasezihlala loBalami.
\v 9 UNkulunkulu wasefika kuBalami, wathi: Ngobani lamadoda alawe?\x + 22.20. Gen. 20.3. Jobe 33.15,16.\x*
\v 10 UBalami wasesithi kuNkulunkulu: UBalaki, indodana kaZipori, inkosi yakoMowabi, ungithumele \add esithi\add*:
\v 11 Khangela, abantu baphumile eGibhithe basibekele ubuso bomhlaba; woza khathesi, ungiqalekisele bona; mhlawumbe ngingaba lamandla okulwa labo, ngibaxotshe.
\v 12 UNkulunkulu wasesithi kuBalami: Ungahambi labo; ungabaqalekisi labobantu, ngoba babusisiwe\x + 23.20.\x*.
\v 13 UBalami wasevuka ekuseni, wathi kuziphathamandla zikaBalaki: Yanini elizweni lakini, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* iyala ukungivumela ukuhamba lani.
\v 14 Ngakho iziphathamandla zakoMowabi zasukuma, zaya kuBalaki, zathi: UBalami uyala ukuhamba lathi.
\p
\v 15 UBalaki wasebuya wathuma njalo iziphathamandla, ezinengi ezidumileyo kulalezo.
\v 16 Zasezifika kuBalami zathi kuye: Utsho njalo uBalaki indodana kaZipori \add uthi\add*: Ake ungavinjwa yilutho ukuza kimi.
\v 17 Ngoba ngizakuhlonipha lokukuhlonipha kakhulu, lakho konke ongitshela khona ngizakwenza. Ngakho ake uze, ngiqalekisela lababantu\x + 22.11.\x*.
\v 18 Kodwa uBalami waphendula wathi encekwini zikaBalaki: Uba uBalaki ebezangipha indlu yakhe igcwele isiliva legolide\x + 24.13.\x*, bengingayikweqa umlayo weN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wami ukwenza okukhulu kumbe okuncinyane\x + 22.38; 23.26; 24.13. 1 Kho. 22.14. 2 Lan. 18.13.\x*.
\v 19 Khathesi-ke, ake lihlale lapha lani lobubusuku, ukuze ngazi ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* izakuthini kimi futhi\x + 22.8.\x*.
\v 20 UNkulunkulu wasesiza kuBalami ebusuku wathi kuye: Uba amadoda efika ukukubiza, sukuma uhambe lawo\x + 22.9.\x*; kodwa kuphela lelolizwi engizalikhuluma kuwe, lona uzalenza\x + 22.35; 23.12,26; 24.13.\x*.
\v 21 UBalami wasesukuma ekuseni, wabophela isihlalo kubabhemikazi wakhe\x + Hlu. 5.10.\x*, wahamba leziphathamandla zakoMowabi.
\p
\v 22 Ulaka lukaNkulunkulu lwavutha ngoba wahamba; ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yayakuma endleleni ukuba yisitha esimelane laye\x + Eks. 4.24.\x*. Njalo wayegade ubabhemikazi wakhe, lenceku zakhe ezimbili zilaye.
\v 23 Ubabhemi waseyibona ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* imi endleleni, lenkemba ehwatshiweyo isesandleni sayo; lobabhemikazi waphambuka endleleni, wangena ensimini. UBalami wasemtshaya ubabhemi ukumphendulela endleleni.
\v 24 Ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yasisima endleleni eminyeneyo yezivini, umduli ngapha lomduli ngapha.
\v 25 Lapho ubabhemikazi ebona ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* wazibandezela emdulini, wabandezela unyawo lukaBalami emdulini; wasemtshaya futhi.
\v 26 Ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yasiqhubeka, yema endaweni eminyeneyo, lapho okwakungelandlela yokuphendukela ngakwesokunene kumbe ngakwesokhohlo.
\v 27 Lapho ubabhemikazi ebona ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd*, walala ngaphansi kukaBalami. Ulaka lukaBalami lwaseluvutha, wasemtshaya ubabhemi ngenduku.
\v 28 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasivula umlomo kababhemikazi\x + 2 Pet. 2.16.\x*, wasesithi kuBalami: Ngenzeni kuwe ukuthi ungitshaye okwalezizikhathi ezintathu?\x + Eks. 23.14.\x*
\v 29 UBalami wasesithi kubabhemikazi: Ngoba ungenze inhlekisa. Kungathi ngabe kulenkemba esandleni sami, ngoba bengizakubulala khathesi.
\v 30 Ubabhemikazi wasesithi kuBalami: Angisuye yini ubabhemi wakho omgade kusukela \add ngi\add*sengowakho kuze kube lamuhla? Ngake ngejwayela ukwenza kanje kuwe yini? Wasesithi: Hatshi.
\v 31 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasivula amehlo kaBalami\x + Gen. 21.19. 2 Kho. 6.17. Luka 24.16,31.\x*, wasebona ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* imi endleleni, lenkemba yayo ihwatshiwe isesandleni sayo; wakhothama wathi mbo ngobuso bakhe phansi\x + Eks. 34.8.\x*.
\v 32 Ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuye: Umtshayeleni ubabhemikazi wakho okwalezizikhathi ezintathu?\x + Eks. 23.14.\x* Khangela, mina ngiphumile ukumelana lawe, ngoba indlela yakho iphambukile kimi\x + Jobe 16.11.\x*;
\v 33 njalo ubabhemikazi wangibona, waphambuka phambi kwami lezizikhathi ezintathu\x + Eks. 23.14.\x*. Ngaphandle kokuthi ephambukile phambi kwami, ngeqiniso khathesi ngabe ngikubulele lawe, ngamgcina yena ephila.
\v 34 UBalami wasesithi engilosini yeN\nd kosi\nd*: Ngonile\x + 1 Sam. 15.24,30; 26.21. 2 Sam. 12.13. Jobe 34.31,32.\x*, ngoba bengingazi ukuthi umi endleleni ukumelana lami. Ngakho-ke uba kukubi emehlweni akho, ngizabuyela futhi.
\v 35 Ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuBalami: Hamba lalawomadoda; kodwa kuphela ilizwi engizalikhuluma kuwe, yilo ozalikhuluma\x + 22.20.\x*. UBalami wasehamba leziphathamandla zikaBalaki.
\p
\v 36 UBalaki esezwile ukuthi uBalami uyeza, waphuma ukuyamhlangabeza emzini wakoMowabi, osemngceleni weArinoni\x + 21.13.\x*, osekucineni komngcele.
\v 37 UBalaki wasesithi kuBalami: Kangithumanga yini lokuthuma kuwe ukukubiza? Kungani ungafikanga kimi? Isibili kangilamandla okukunika udumo yini?\x + 22.17; 24.11.\x*
\v 38 UBalami wasesithi kuBalaki: Khangela, ngifikile kuwe. Khathesi ngilamandla isibili okukhuluma loba yini na? Ilizwi uNkulunkulu alifaka emlonyeni wami, yilo engizalikhuluma\x + 22.18.\x*.
\v 39 UBalami wasehamba loBalaki, basebefika eKiriyathi-Huzothi.
\v 40 UBalaki wasehlaba izinkabi lezimvu, wathumela kuBalami lakuziphathamandla ezazilaye.
\v 41 Kwasekusithi ekuseni uBalaki wamthatha uBalami, wamenyusela endaweni eziphakemeyo zikaBhali\x + 21.20; Dute. 12.2.\x*, ukuthi abone elapho ukucina kwabantu.
